cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.CR 

This paper is about face recognition, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses machine learning methods (cs.LG) and deep learning (cs.AI) for face recognition. Additionally, the paper involves the use of a database (cs.MM) and discusses the limitations and challenges of face recognition (cs.CR).
